Detailed Description

Collection of organs.

vtkOrganCollection represents and provides methods to manipulate a list of Organs (i.e., vtkOrgan and subclasses). The list is unsorted and duplicate entries are not prevented.

See also:
vtkCollection, vtkOrgan

vtkOrgan * vtkOrganCollection::GetNextOrgan (  ) 

Return the next organism on the list.

Get the organ at the pointer position. Beware of calling InitTraversal() to init the pointer. NULL is returned when the collection is exhausted.
